name: Circuit Launch
description: The **Circuit Launch** map is a re-creation of the indoor [F1TENTH](https://f1tenth.org/) autonomous racing track used for [DIY Robocars events](https://www.meetup.com/DIYRobocars/) at [Circuit Launch](https://www.circuitlaunch.com/) in Oakland, CA. This map is intended for use with 1/10 scale vehicles such as the [F1TENTH Traxxis vehicle](/vehicles/profile/3bb4c2eb-82d3-4ee3-8ebb-2bdbcf6e88ea).
